    "a hard ceiling, include maxMeanNs (ns) or maxMsPerFrame (ms) \u2014",
    "maxMsPerFrame uses perFrameNs automatically for frameRun benchmarks.",
    "",
    "Numbers captured on Linux x86_64 dev hardware (Dart 3.11.4 /",
